    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about \"starting again\" though. the rubble is all there is. people only liked the version of me that was successful. now that the prestige is gone, the connections are gone, the respect is gone. even the people who say they care... they're just looking at a ghost. it feels like the world has already moved on and decided i don't exist anymore. why should i keep trying to find \"ground\" when there's nothing but ash?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
